title: TANGO`S M`DANCERS
description: SIGNS OF M`DANCERS  1. M`DANCER understands autenthicity as the following of its unique individuality but not to mode or to public. 2. M`DANCER attempts to watch itself, partner and environment through the heart, but not - the mind. 3.  M`DANCER attempts to dances meditatively, i.e., in the relaxation, to keep totaly watch over, and in acceptance without nondivision. 4. M`DANCER listens music with heart, but not with mind. He forgets now itself as the mind. 5. M`DANCER dances von his unique individuality. 6. M`DANCER is approached now each moment spontaneous to responses to his unique individuality. 7. Body visualises now not only rhythm and phrasing of musics, but also its tunefulness, overtones, dynamics and polyphony. In the motion of bodies it is possible to see impulsiveness, plasticity, softness, liquidity and continuity, uncommon figures and the sequences... 8. In the dance of M`DANCER not to see show, demonstrativeness, making, overcoming, achievement... Hi is totaly absorbed in dance, moves freely and easily, as if playing. 9. In the dance of M`DANCERS are visible attentiveness and love for the partner. 10. Dance does not strain M`DANCER. His respiration remains inaudible and calm. I will glad to discuss with each these signs.
